    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタインデー前のある日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（もうこんな時間か……早く帰ろう）\n（……ん？　まだ誰か残ってるのか？）",
      "startTime": 8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "おや、{user}君\nこんな時間まで仕事なの？",
      "startTime": 16.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ。葵も遅くまでお疲れ様\n一人で練習してたのか？",
      "startTime": 22.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐバレンタインイベントがあるから\nその練習",
      "startTime": 26.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "本番のステージで、思うように体が動かない\nなんて訳にはいかないからね",
      "startTime": 31.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "出演が決まった訳じゃないのに\nやる気満々じゃないか",
      "startTime": 36.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁね\nこころが凄くやる気になってるんだよ",
      "startTime": 39.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "さすが、リズノワの頼れる先輩は違うな",
      "startTime": 42.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "……とはいえ、さすがにもう遅いし\n今日はそろそろ切り上げることにするよ",
      "startTime": 51.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それなら寮まで送るよ。夜道を一人じゃ危険だろ？",
      "startTime": 54.1,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}